In mathematical physics, the gamma matrices, 
  
    
      
         
        
          {
          
            
              γ
              
                0
              
            
            ,
            
              γ
              
                1
              
            
            ,
            
              γ
              
                2
              
            
            ,
            
              γ
              
                3
              
            
          
          }
        
         
