    {\displaystyle \ \psi \ }
   is a Dirac spinor.
Switching to Feynman notation, the Dirac equation is

  
    
      
         
        (
        i
        
          ∂
          
          
          
          
            /
          
        
        −
        m
        )
        ψ
        =
        0
         
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ (i{\partial \!\!\!/}-m)\psi =0~.}

