Charge conjugation
The charge conjugation operator, in any basis, may be defined as

  
    
      
        C
        
          γ
          
            μ
          
        
        
          C
          
            −
            1
          
        
        =
        −
        (
        
          γ
          
            μ
          
        
        
          )
          
            
              T
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle C\gamma _{\mu }C^{-1}=-(\gamma _{\mu })^{\textsf {T}}}
  where 
  
    
      
        (
        ⋅
        
          )
          
            
              T
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle (\cdot )^{\textsf {T}}}
   denotes the matrix transpose. The explicit form that 
  
    
      
        C
      
    
    {\displaystyle C}
   takes is dependent on the specific representation chosen for the gamma matrices (its form expressed as product of the gamma matrices is representation dependent, while it can be seen 
  
    
      
         
        C
        =
        i
        
          γ
          
            0
          
        
        
          γ
          
            2
          
        
         
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ C=i\gamma ^{0}\gamma ^{2}\ }
   in the Dirac basis:

  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                C
              
              
                
                =
                
                  
                    (
                    
                      
                        
                          0
                        
                        
                           
                           
                           
                          0
                        
                        
                          0
                        
                        
                          −
                          1
                        
                      
                      
                        
                          0
                        
                        
                           
                           
                           
