   with the appropriate identity in terms of gamma matrices.

Other representations
The matrices are also sometimes written using the 2×2 identity matrix, 
  
    
      
        
          I
          
            2
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle I_{2}}
  , and

  
    
      
        
          γ
          
            k
          
        
