Majorana basis
There is also the Majorana basis, in which all of the Dirac matrices are imaginary, and the spinors and Dirac equation are real. Regarding the Pauli matrices, the basis  can be written as

  
    
      
        
          
            
              
                
                  γ
                  
                    0
                  
                
              
              
                
                =
                
                  
